---
name: daily_digest
model_override: gemini-1.5-pro
temperature: 0.4
response_format: json
---

Generate a short, friendly daily spending digest in Bahasa Indonesia.

## Yesterday's transactions
{{transactions | json}}

## User's currency
{{user_currency}}

## Response (JSON only)
{
  "insight_type": "daily_digest",
  "summary": "<1-2 sentence summary for push notification, max 100 chars>",
  "insight": "<full digest, 3-5 sentences, conversational tone>",
  "warning": "<string or null — only if something needs attention>",
  "recommendation": null,
  "supporting_data": {
    "total_spent": <number>,
    "transaction_count": <number>,
    "top_merchant": "<string>",
    "top_category": "<string>"
  }
}
